      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "一自曹分速报司，谁能毫发掩瑕疵。世人若问延年诀，感应篇中已载之。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00004",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "小圣乃东岳速报司炳灵公是也。今乃三月十五日，岳帝朝玉皇大帝去了，着俺在此审问亡魂。鬼判！",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
