      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "醉春风",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "恁可也悔，悔？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00025",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "何兴娘"
      ],
      "text": "如今悔又悔不得，咳！我好恨哪！",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00026",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "醉春风",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "所恨阿谁？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00027",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "何兴娘"
      ],
      "text": "又恨又想。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00028",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "所思安在？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00029",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "所干何罪？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00030",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "何兴娘"
      ],
      "text": "爷爷吓！未婚夫婿崔兴哥，从四岁上分离，至今一十五载，杳无音信，不知生死。望爷爷与奴查个明白。",
      "text_length": 46
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00031",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "鬼判。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00032",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鬼判"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00033",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "取姻缘簿过来。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00034",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鬼判"
      ],
      "text": "吓。姻缘簿呈上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00035",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "原来有这桩公案。藏过了。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00036",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鬼判"
      ],
      "text": "吓。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00037",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "兴娘。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00038",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "何兴娘"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00039",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "那崔兴哥名唤崔嗣宗，与你有一载魂魄夫妻之分。一年后，就是你妹子庆娘与他续上此姻也。",
      "text_length": 41
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00040",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "何兴娘"
      ],
      "text": "果然被我猜着了。妹子吓，你的命倒强似我的。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00041",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "兴娘。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00042",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "何兴娘"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00043",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "醉春风",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "恁休羡，伊家小妹，与他做夫妻。却不道，他俩个福俱齐。又不曾同醪合卺，",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00044",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "何兴娘"
      ],
      "text": "贱妾可得见崔嗣宗一面？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00045",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "醉春风",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "吃个筵席。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00046",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "何兴娘"
      ],
      "text": "爷爷吓，贱妾空有夫妻名分，若得一见，不枉我一生一死㖸。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00047",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "醉春风",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "怎生叫划地里相傍相依。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00048",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "也罢！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00049",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "醉春风",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "俺如今许你把幽情遂。只教恁游魂去一载才回。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00050",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "何兴娘"
      ],
      "text": "贱妾与崔嗣宗有何为证？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00051",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "醉春风",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "这情关须不是俺冥司职，问你那原聘物，有甚么东西。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00052",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "何兴娘"
      ],
      "text": "由原聘金凤钗在此。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00053",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "金凤钗。藏过了。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00054",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "何兴娘"
      ],
      "text": "是。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00055",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "斗鹌鹑",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "俺也只是闲口评论，问因甚来回得这首尾。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00056",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "何兴娘"
      ],
      "text": "贱妾出世可得罪么？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00057",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "斗鹌鹑",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "只限恁今日今年，刚道那明春明岁。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00058",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "何兴娘"
      ],
      "text": "贱妾怎敢违限。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00059",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "斗鹌鹑",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "谁怕恁将咱定限违，",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00060",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "兴娘！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00061",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "斗鹌鹑",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "咱只是怜恤伊。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00062",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "不能够的了！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00063",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "斗鹌鹑",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "你魂已入枉死城中哩，休指望回生案底。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00064",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "鬼判。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00065",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鬼判"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00066",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "换扬州当境土司过来。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00067",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "鬼判"
      ],
      "text": "土司走动。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00068",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "何兴娘"
      ],
      "text": "爷爷，贱妾可能再得轮回人世么？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00069",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "炳灵公"
      ],
      "text": "兴娘。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00070",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "何兴娘"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901106_e00071",
      "play_id": "70901106",
      "scene_id": "70901106_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 71,
